data.description: **Motivated Sellers!!**  Discover the epitome of easy living in this beautifully designed split foyer home, where cozy and functionality harmoniously converge. Located close to Lake White and an easy drive into town, this home has thoughtful features that redefine comfort and convenience. Upon entering, the upper-level host the first of 2 living spaces, 2 bedrooms and the beautiful kitchen with an abundance of cabinetry. Downstairs you will find a large family room with an updated fireplace, the 3rd bedroom and the relaxing sunroom, which is perfect for all seasons.  And let us not forget the spacious patio for outdoor entertaining!  This home is a must see!  Call to schedule your private showing!
